### 2. Color System (Vietnamese Cultural)

**CSS Variables** (src/styles.css:4-20):
```css
:root {
  /* Primary Neutrals */
  --bg: #ffffff;
  --surface: #f4efec;
  --text: #1a1a1a;
  --text-muted: #4e4c4f;
  --border: #9f8d8d;

  /* Vietnamese Period Colors */
  --period-cds: #1f2937;        /* Cổ đại (Ancient) */
  --period-pks: #dc2626;        /* Phong kiến (Feudal) */
  --period-cds-modern: #eabb00; /* Cận đại (Modern) */
  --period-hds: #16a34a;        /* Hiện đại (Contemporary) */

  /* Accent Colors */
  --accent-primary: #d9ae8e;    /* Floating button default */
  --accent-emphasis: #c41e3a;   /* Button hover, emphasis */
}
```

**Contrast Verification**:
- All period colors: ≥4.5:1 on white (WCAG AA)
- Primary text: 15.3:1 on white (WCAG AAA)

